name: Ukraine
description:
Wrote a whole lot of text and deleted it again as it feels wrong to ramble while one of the biggest catastrophes in recent modern history unfolds before the eyes of the world.

So basically, this is just a very humble try to create something akin to art while being horrified all day by the news from Ukraine. My thoughts are with the people of Ukraine. You are not forgotten.

This is a free 100 edition run.
